    title: "The Quilt of Small Repairs",
    author: "Khyati Srivastava",
    slug: "the-quilt-of-small-repairs",
    category: "Drama",
    emoji: "🧵",
    excerpt: "A patchwork quilt passed down through four generations carries a stitched repair for every hard year the family survived — and it's Nadia's turn to add one.",
